  SpeakerName: Dialogue
  lines:
  - Salutations my good sir. I'm in need of assistance with an outlet in my bathroom.
  - It does not work and I like to charge my devices when I am taking a shower.
  - "The outlet is right next to my sink it\u2019s really easy to find would appreciate
    your assistance   "
